										| “Set of message board with message paper vector”
										| by <a href="http://freedesignfile.com/">freedesignfile</a>
										| Licensed under CC-BY
									li
										| “Set of pipeline parts vector”
										| by <a href="http://freedesignfile.com/">freedesignfile</a>
										| Licensed under CC-BY
									li
